”Alexa, start birthday is coming”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: birthday is coming
des:
Turn on the skill and Alexa will quickly let you know how many days are left until your Birthday. 
It's a cool way to get pumped to hit your personal goals and act on your intentions before your solar revolution arrives. 
Set it as a part of your morning routine to help you stay motivated!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
